description: Experience breathtaking ocean and city views from this coveted corner 2 bedroom + den at Twenty Two Liberty. This exceptional home features floor-to-ceiling windows, custom closets, soaring 10 foot ceilings, Lutron shades, hardwood floors, and a private balcony off of the living room. A gracious foyer welcomes you into this meticulously designed residence, leading to a gorgeous open-concept kitchen appointed with top of the line appliances by Wolf, Miele, and Subzero. The primary suite features two walls of glass and includes a spa-like bathroom adorned in Italian marble with a double vanity, soaking tub, and glass shower. A generously sized bonus space works as an office or bonus room for guests. Twenty-Two Liberty amenities include 24 hour concierge and doorman, magnificent clubroom with terrace overlooking the harbor, fitness center, caterer’s kitchen, and conference room. Includes 2 side-be side deeded parking spaces.
